<p><strong>段治卿仲秋闲吟杂集</strong></p>
<p><strong>观竹</strong></p>
<p>竹海涛涛</p>
<p>悄入云</p>
<p>竿竿亮节</p>
<p>噼叭音</p>
<p>忽有小鸟</p>
<p>远飞过</p>
<p>一路哨声</p>
<p>横笛吹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201002/58d039a9c740475293b3c78ff0622b83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
